{
  "id": "RAW_cc067b61",
  "title": "自从换这走查方式，前端再没一句废话",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&mid=2247532049&idx=1&sn=d13f926bd68798b0ae31afb9f0a4731a",
  "date": "2025-10-13 00:20:00",
  "author": "体验进阶",
  "siteName": "体验进阶",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a048112&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxaQ3cJgILeFCAgaFjkVy10ErcJAMw5rWaauIcVhcBBae2fFNVOmlkZw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">做设计工作多年，我很少遇到把页面还原度做得特别好的前端开发。能够让我肉眼看不出毛病，就已经算相当好了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">当一个页面的还原度差到肉眼能看出明显的问题时，那就真的不得不提出修改建议了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048309\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=188b19ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxTTKrDE0oUWbHUOcyKTA2ak2qeZPYoicuCN5XyYd93xGp4jCL3VDK7Sw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">像是上图，按钮和描述文字的间距太窄了，如果只说“太窄”肯定不行，要给出精确的数值才好。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是除了间距之外，行高也有问题，还得把行高说一下。这样一个个数值报出来，就很麻烦了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">而且网页端通常会有弹性布局，页面宽度和方案不同的话，还会影响判断。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048310\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e5855227&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxRa1100LL9VhI2yZJ4LbgsmbfGj7JfXKnt5LOZOWxaO6dukSXpfY1ibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">网页端的还原度走查，最好的走查方法是用浏览器自带的开发者工具，可以直接看到所有元素的</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">样式</span><span leaf=\"\">和布局属性。这其实也是前端自己debug的方法。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxCzgJd8TUJBKS1o0hDVOpt3vv4BMkCPia1IpZS9ueY9ra9CNZZujsZwA/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"361\" data-imgfileid=\"100048312\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-w=\"1080\" data-type=\"gif\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2874a68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxCzgJd8TUJBKS1o0hDVOpt3vv4BMkCPia1IpZS9ueY9ra9CNZZujsZwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">App的话麻烦一点，这个后面再说。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgagap2mhkt\" style=\"font-size: 28px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgagap381hje\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">打开方法</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">以下就用Chrome为例。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">打开网页后，在页面任意位置点击鼠标右键，然后选择菜单中的「检查」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048313\" data-ratio=\"0.8885542168674698\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"664\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3f7bb10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxUB1bYYqWSnq7Ip0DJdeUU20NMwiaxk4l6vPKibAKuLu36ToJEUIervPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">还可以点击浏览器地址栏右侧最边缘的「…」更多菜单，选择「更多工具-开发者工具」。这个操作步骤麻烦一点，而且进去后还要选择「元素」页签才行，还是右键菜单简单。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">进入下面这个视图后，第一步建议把尺寸（主要是宽度）设置为跟设计稿一致（例如下图设置的是1280），这样容易对比一些。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048315\" data-ratio=\"0.17037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=933daff6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxhcRbc8jz3vYNt9lzVx3FNbia2kqUnkknNgwV99Dc4bga5gq8vmNkPaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">然后就可以开始走查了。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgagap2mhkt\" style=\"font-size: 28px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgagap381hje\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">走查样式</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">在右上角的代码栏顶部，点击左端的箭头图标。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">然后你在左侧的网页上移动鼠标，就可以看到各个元素的样式了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048317\" data-ratio=\"0.35462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb149d2d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxf28eMeQDnCFma3kJBPDRoOCW2Da7lxQ5whIOWpR3rVoFl6AunJ509w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果是文字，可以检查的样式有长宽（气泡右上角的数字）、颜色（Color）、字号和字体（Font）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048319\" data-ratio=\"0.6472222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81895438&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxvCOJAaFJZPVs6x2luz0yauCOBzSZMg3xcMUArKTicdsustABibkRBOhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至，它还检查了包容性设计检查：Contrast代表背景色和文字的色彩对比是否足够清晰；Name和Role是给</span><span leaf=\"\">屏幕阅读器用的</span><span leaf=\"\">；Keyboard-focusable是给纯键盘操作用的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果是图片，最有用的信息就是尺寸的：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048320\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9b6abea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxpGhoWNfZh1fkrMpc6OJAc2tYdw0rJSCZI1FPfvIyASibMGc5xxFgIicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这样不比肉眼走查轻松多了？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果哪里属性不对，只需截2个图，一个是网页端的样式数据，另一个是方案稿的样式设置，无需多言。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">次数多了，前端开发也知道要怎么看设计稿了，不再乱写样式属性。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgagap2mhkt\" style=\"font-size: 28px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgagap381hje\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">走查间距</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">鼠标在网页上滑动的时候，可以看到悬停元素上，多了一些格子，可以用来检查布局。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">中间的蓝色区块加上绿色区块，就是元素本体占据的空间。例如下图，这两个区块加起来的尺寸就是797*97像素。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048327\" data-ratio=\"0.1968810916179337\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1026\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=389554bd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxz5qOEXCM20AWCoJPyxLTBKAYnTibqytBkvJ9Q5dVjmdxAFlztRg1lwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">其中，绿色区块代表元素的内边距（padding）。相当于Figma自动布局里最底下的两个数值：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048322\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8577405857740585\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"478\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=76f9ca22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxRVuKGNrn1sWLrKPgdzQkKg87cXhYYm4M25ZhzFsWTfCJ4nb2Ktrx7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">元素的子元素，是不允许进入内边距范畴的。因此，蓝色区域才是子元素的活动范围。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">元素外面的橙色区块，是元素的外边距（Margin）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048328\" data-ratio=\"0.3302752293577982\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"654\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18065040&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrx87JxyiacnfwAOjq1q2aNBNkV1RicCVeUSTX82ASK85Nqb3lM5kTz9ZGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个东西在Figma里面不存在，所以这里特别解释一下。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">外边距相当于给元素找了一个透明的结界，不论是旁边别的同级元素还是父元素，都不得入内。这相当于让元素的实际占位，比本体更大一些。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">例如上图元素本体尺寸为26*23像素，加上外边距后，实际占位就变成了45*47像素。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">内边距（padding）和外边距（Margin）的数值，在气泡里写清楚了，但是不太好理解。可以去代码栏的「样式」模块里，翻到底部，看看这张图：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048329\" data-ratio=\"0.7849898580121704\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"986\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8984d4a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxSfUG3qGH1QYHlPYfvSOff0xmMk2B04oiaDb9icB7LF1GKXgZgPu5kmbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有一种紫色的虚线框呢？这个是flex布局容器，这个布局方法和Figma的自动布局有点类似，但功能更加丰富。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048330\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5662650602409639\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"166\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2328ed95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrx2jPJCamxMhKSGaspJjd6JicxNpDun8wDeVnqCLTdBNQayfLn48OcScw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">布局规则就很难在这里讲清楚了，有兴趣的话可以参加我们的《前端认知训练营》，里面除了flex之外，还有很多对设计师有用的前端知识的讲解和练习。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048336\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=310e1d96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrx3pcHAqFKl5PurhXSuNIw94xyNZlhMiaKg862fcaxGibibMkCGH1ZA0Qiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgagap2mhkt\" style=\"font-size: 28px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgagap381hje\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">修改属性</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">有时前端还原度的问题，是由多种数值不准确导致的。你无法确定是不是改了某个数值，就万事大吉了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">所以，你可以直接用开发者工具修改属性。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">尺寸和边距是最简单的，前面提过的那张表，上面的数字双击后可以直接修改：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048331\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5679442508710801\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"574\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1445c6b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxh3YmuKzfXAgOQH2NiaQyl6TNNsibAR82OdBiawQU0sgFjicNUuMXV4icfOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">样式呢？你就要翻到「样式」模块的顶部，去找CSS代码了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048332\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7266666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7924fab0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxe2EKPbWic2cicdPOLCCptSObNcIU6IZbNvfwYrtfr6QRGd7X8XgRJLqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">例如上图，color代表字体颜色、font代表字体、text-decoration代表文本装饰（常用来做下划线）。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">例如，行高是line-height，你找到这个词，然后把冒号后面的数值改一下就好了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">其它经常走查的样式还有</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">行高（line-height）</span><span leaf=\"\">、边框（border）、背景（background）……</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">都是比较好理解的英文，但具体的代码写法，就需要真正有点前端基础才行了——我们即将开始的《前端认知训练营》就有教，还带着写一些简单的代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048337\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f75ebe35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEht6DxGBibMEbuDQlekkgrxek5VNBqDtHbic396Jer5XXDBDr1j4O19Wfass4ibibhUpSbIOibPxeoBdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">新人扫码后可以领取优惠券，不过当天注册的因为系统bug领不了，可以微信zoeyz0001手动操作或隔天再试：</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048307\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35185185185185186\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 676.992px !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7dfb921&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCGlEuPon98icn1kTjgInYpCoa9IrCibWhYtkuLUXn9xFEQeib65UfcbZc1h7ia7ia6ibbsz4aia1WAbKyDjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D16\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">这样走查效果怎样？</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果是一眼就能看出的大问题，那说明前端太糊弄，直接开怼就好了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但很多情况下，前端还原度并非一眼可见，但还是存在很多偏差。这个时候，用开发者工具走查效率和精准度都更高。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">而且，你口述或打字说哪里有问题要怎么改，很麻烦，对方还不耐烦。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">要是把属性对比截图发过去，对方就很难有脾气了。其实开发大多挺认死理的，用这种方式更好沟通。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">App也能这么走查吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">原生开发的页面，只能用开发工具来检查，比较麻烦。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是很多App为了省事，除了一级核心页面外，会用大量的 WebView 网页开发。例如图文资讯页、营销活动、</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">小程序等第三方服务页……</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这些页面，可以使用工具来做类似的走查。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">官方的工具有：</span><span leaf=\"\">Chrome DevTools 支持安卓 app 的&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">WebView 检查；</span><span leaf=\"\">Safari Web Inspector 支持 iOS App 的 WebView检查。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果想要一个工具搞定不同 app，也有第三方工具可用，例如&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">Web Debug X 等。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果有兴趣，我以后再找机会介绍。</span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细介绍了设计师或产品经理如何利用浏览器开发者工具进行网页设计还原度走查，以提高沟通效率和精确性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细介绍了设计师或产品经理如何利用浏览器开发者工具进行网页设计还原度走查，以提高沟通效率和精确性。",
  "summary": "本文旨在解决设计与前端开发之间在页面还原度沟通上的痛点，旨在实现“前端再没一句废话”的沟通效果。作者指出传统肉眼走查效率低且不精确，容易引发沟通障碍。文章核心建议是设计师和产品经理应掌握使用浏览器自带的开发者工具（以 Chrome 为例），通过检查元素的样式、尺寸、间距（内边距和外边距）等属性，实现精确、客观的走查。文中提供了详细的操作步骤，包括打开开发者工具、设置模拟尺寸、检查样式属性和间距、以及临时修改属性进行验证。这种方法不仅能提升走查效率和准确性，更能通过提供数据化和视觉化的截图证据，有效减少前端开发过程中的无效沟通和争执。文章还简要提及了 App 中 WebView 页面的类似走查方法。然而，文章末尾插入了多处课程推广内容，影响了内容的纯粹性。",
